  <mmd:title xml:lang="en">NORCE NDVI for Svalbard</mmd:title>
  <mmd:abstract xml:lang="en">Daily NDVI estimates since 2000 for Svalbard. Only areas with summer NDVI &gt; 0.0, other areas has -1.001 in value. A new version of the production algorithm is used from 2022 and onwards. </mmd:abstract>
